1964;;Woman of Straw;;British;;Basil Dearden;;Gina Lollobrigida, Sean Connery, Ralph Richardson;;mystery;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Woman_of_Straw;;Connery's character Anthony Richmond schemes to get the fortune of his tyrannical, wheelchair-using tycoon uncle Charles Richmond (Richardson) by persuading Maria, a nurse he employs (Lollobrigida), to marry him. After his uncle's demise Maria becomes a murder suspect. Lollobrigida's character is the Woman of Straw of the title.